{{SupportPage|vendor=Encore|model=ENHWI-N2}} OEM Cameo WLN-2206 ([https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=18314 see also here]), Atheros AP81 based, similar to other Cameo manuf. models such as the [[TRENDnet TEW-632BRP]], [[TRENDnet TEW-652BRP V1.xR]], [[D-Link DIR-615 rev C1]], and the [[D-Link DIR-615 rev C2]] [http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=142564 On the DD-WRT forums] :The board ID for this device appears to be AP81-AR9130-RT-070614-01. The default SSID for this device is presumed to be '''ENHWI-N2'''. WiGLE has ~50 entries for this device, all with 00:18:E7 (Cameo) OUIs.
